"\n"
"\n"
"<5.au_ad>Link...<6.te_si><7.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<8.au_ad><9.te_si>Link...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<10.te_si><11.au_ad><12.te_si>I have watched your journey. Every step.\n"
"You have overcome every challenge with\n"
"great courage.\n"
"<13.te_si><14.au_ad><15.te_si>With the power that you have attained...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<16.te_si><17.au_ad><18.te_si>I am certain you can defeat\n"
